sentences.en: When a noun ends with a consonant such as -o,s, z, ch, sh, and x, you also have to add -es.

sentences.en: Anyone knowing the whereabouts of Mr. Jones, or having information which may lead to his location, is requested to report to any police station or to his family at the address : 16 CH Road.
